{"tid":1829741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿姆斯特丹為負債年輕人制訂生涯規劃　完成求職求學目標可註銷部分債務","createTime":"2020-01-19T04:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T05:28:17.000Z","uid":306664,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87f7b2119d1e22d4da9267fa294896229f2436e1","tid":1829741,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"民主好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200118/s00005/1579357054380/%e9%98%bf%e5%a7%86%e6%96%af%e7%89%b9%e4%b8%b9%e7%82%ba%e8%b2%a0%e5%82%b5%e5%b9%b4%e8%bc%95%e4%ba%ba%e5%88%b6%e8%a8%82%e7%94%9f%e6%b6%af%e8%a6%8f%e5%8a%83-%e5%ae%8c%e6%88%90%e6%b1%82%e8%81%b7%e6%b1%82%e5%ad%b8%e7%9b%ae%e6%a8%99%e5%8f%af%e8%a8%bb%e9%8a%b7%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86%e5%82%b5%e5%8b%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200118%2Fs00005%2F1579357054380%2F%25e9%2598%25bf%25e5%25a7%2586%25e6%2596%25af%25e7%2589%25b9%25e4%25b8%25b9%25e7%2582%25ba%25e8%25b2%25a0%25e5%2582%25b5%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25bc%2595%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2588%25b6%25e8%25a8%2582%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%25b6%25af%25e8%25a6%258f%25e5%258a%2583-%25e5%25ae%258c%25e6%2588%2590%25e6%25b1%2582%25e8%2581%25b7%25e6%25b1%2582%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%259b%25ae%25e6%25a8%2599%25e5%258f%25af%25e8%25a8%25bb%25e9%258a%25b7%25e9%2583%25a8%25e5%2588%2586%25e5%2582%25b5%25e5%258b%2599&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1FKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=45b76a1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200118%2Fs00005%2F1579357054380%2F%25e9%2598%25bf%25e5%25a7%2586%25e6%2596%25af%25e7%2589%25b9%25e4%25b8%25b9%25e7%2582%25ba%25e8%25b2%25a0%25e5%2582%25b5%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25bc%2595%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2588%25b6%25e8%25a8%2582%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%25b6%25af%25e8%25a6%258f%25e5%258a%2583-%25e5%25ae%258c%25e6%2588%2590%25e6%25b1%2582%25e8%2581%25b7%25e6%25b1%2582%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%259b%25ae%25e6%25a8%2599%25e5%258f%25af%25e8%25a8%25bb%25e9%258a%25b7%25e9%2583%25a8%25e5%2588%2586%25e5%2582%25b5%25e5%258b%2599&h=880288f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200118/s00005/1579357054380/%e9%98%bf%e5%a7%86%e6%96%af%e7%89%b9%e4%b8%b9%e7%82%ba%e8%b2%a0%e5%82%b5%e5%b9%b4%e8%bc%95%e4%ba%ba%e5%88%b6%e8%a8%82%e7%94%9f%e6%b6%af%e8%a6%8f%e5%8a%83-%e5%ae%8c%e6%88%90%e6%b1%82%e8%81%b7%e6%b1%82%e5%ad%b8%e7%9b%ae%e6%a8%99%e5%8f%af%e8%a8%bb%e9%8a%b7%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86%e5%82%b5%e5%8b%99</a><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭首都阿姆斯特丹市政府宣布於下月推出計劃，協助受學生貸款等拖累負債的年輕人度身訂做生涯規劃，以註銷部分債務的方式誘使他們完成求職或求學目標，務求協助他們加強裝備自己，避免遭債務枷鎖拖累一生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿姆斯特丹的「青年無債起步」（Young people debt-free start）計劃，對象是3年內無能力還清債務的約2萬名18至27歲居民。市政府信託銀行將與計劃參與者的「債主」磋商，游說債主同意以750歐元（約6460港元）轉移債務至信託銀行，相關年輕人可以優惠低利率繼續向信託銀行還債。與此同時，參與者會獲分配跟進個案的「教練」，在其輔助下重組債務及規劃未來，包括訂立目標，例如找到工作或上新課程。他們一旦達標，銀行便給他們註銷更多債務。<br />\n<br />\n副市長穆爾曼（Marjolein Moorman）道：「債務造成巨大壓力。以年輕人而言，負債通常決定他們的未來。這些年輕人之中，大部分一開始就處於不利位置，而且因為霉運或無知，置身倘無援助將難以翻身的局面。」<br />\n<br />\n阿姆斯特丹官方數據顯示，該市18歲至34歲的人當中，有34％負債，由拖欠小額債務如上月手機帳單，到積欠數萬歐元不等。荷蘭學生的平均債務由2015年的12,400歐元（近10.7萬港元），增至2019年的13,700歐元（11.8萬港元）；同期背負學生貸款債務的人數增加38.8萬，至140萬人。<br />\n<br />\n（荷蘭時報/荷蘭新聞/themayor.eu/CNBC）"},{"pid":"db09e761807e4e83ed76fb0a3b5902feaf928d8c","tid":1829741,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"唔關民主事，美國一樣有學債，中國更加有祼貸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0eb2a95ae67279a033bfddaa3e1fa31c1306340","tid":1829741,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"我諗起報紙話香港學生唔還GRANT LOAN<br />\n建制派同藍絲話要告到班學生破產"},{"pid":"45f7259735a280f58cb435050e1f04c4d518e3de","tid":1829741,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:21:17.000Z","msg":"生涯規劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ed1450179f6454b6bc1709fc61de531533f328","tid":1829741,"uid":207247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"肯為自己人民好既政府<br />\n<br />\n反觀林鄭同中共，好想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}